{"word":"δῶμα","slug":"δῶμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n29773\" key=\"dw=ma\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">δῶμα</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ατος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">δέμω</etym>) <sense id=\"n29773.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">house</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πατρώϊον ἵκετο δ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:44\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.44</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc.; mainly poet., but once in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:62\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author>, <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.62</biblScope> </bibl> (pl.), and in late Prose (v. infr.), but never in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram> </gramGrp> Prose: also, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">chief room, hall</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">θάλαμον καὶ δ. καὶ</foreign> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">αὐλήν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:316\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.316</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:17:329\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform